    dc:description "Figure 3. Colobomatus pteroisi sp. nov., adult female. (A) Habitus, ventral; (B) antennule, ventral; (C) tip of anterior cephalic process, ventral; (D) pair of papillae anterior to oral area, ventral; (E) buccal capsule and mouthparts, ventral; (F) leg 1, ventrolateral; (G) leg 2, ventrolateral; (H) leg 3, ventrolateral; (I) tip of posterior thoracic process, ventral. Abbreviations: A, antenna; la, labium; mx, maxillule; Mx, maxilla." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4632027/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

